The soul instantly heals you for 498,357, and grants you up to 9,477 Critical Strike for 16 sec. You gain more Critical Strike from lower health targets. (2 Min Cooldown)

description: A death-defying concoction made with Mama's secret recipe to numb your sense of self-preservation.
